quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  56,39,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,40,Na benshi mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,41,Naho abantu b’ibumoso; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihano by’abantu b’ibumoso)
  56,42,Bazaba bari mu muyaga utwika ndetse n’amazi yatuye
  56,43,No mu gicucu cy’umwotsi w’umukara
  56,44,(Icyo gicucu) nta mbeho kizatanga ndetse nta n’icyiza kizagiturukaho
  56,45,"Mu by’ukuri, mbere bari babayeho mu buzima bwo kwinezeza (bigomeka kuri Allah)"
  56,46,Kandi bajyaga batsimbarara ku byaha bihambaye (ntibagire umugambi wo kubyicuza)
  56,47,"Kandi bajyaga bavuga bati \" Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka n’amagufa (akabora), tuzazurwa koko"
  56,48,N’abakurambere bacu (bazazurwa) se
  56,49,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Yego) rwose, abo hambere n’abo hanyuma"
  56,50,"Bazakoranywa ku munsi uzwi, wagenwe (umunsi w’imperuka)"
  56,51,Nuko mwe abayobye mukanahinyura ukuri
  56,52,Rwose muzarya ku giti cya Zaqumu
  56,53,Maze mucyuzuze inda
  56,54,Mukirenzeho amazi yatuye
  56,55,Muzayanywa nk’ingamiya zinywa zidashira inyota
  56,56,Iryo ni ryo zimano ryabo ku munsi w’ibihembo
  56,57,Ni twe twabaremye. Nonese kuki mutemera (izuka)
  56,58,Ese mutekereza iki ku matembabuzi (amasohora) musohora
  56,59,Ese ni mwe muyarema cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,60,Ni twe twabageneye urupfu kandi ntitwananirwa
  56,61,"Kubasimbuza abameze nka mwe, maze tukabaremamo (amashusho y’) ibindi mutazi"
  56,62,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, mwamenye ukuremwa (kwanyu) kwa mbere. Nonese kuki mutibuka"
  56,63,Ese ntimubona ibyo muhinga
  56,64,"Ese ni mwe mubiha kumera no gukura, cyangwa ni twe tubikora"
  56,65,"Tubishatse twabigira ubushingwe, maze mugakomeza kumirwa"
  56,66,"(Muvuga muti) \"Rwose twaruhiye ubusa"
  56,67,Ahubwo twimwe (ibintu byose)
  56,68,Ese ntimubona amazi munywa
  56,69,Ese ni mwe muyamanura mu bicu cyangwa ni twe tuyamanura
  56,70,"Iyo tuza kubishaka, twari kuyagira urwunyunyu (ntanyobwe). Nonese kuki mudashimira (Allah)"
  56,71,Ese ntimubona umuriro mucana
  56,72,Ese ni mwe mwaremye igiti cyawo (muwukomoramo) cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,73,"Ni twe twawugize urwibutso (rw’umuriro wa Jahanamu), ndetse n’ingirakamaro ku bagenzi (n’abandi bose bawukeneye)"
  56,74,"Ngaho singiza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"